    "body": "The correct network config should be `1337` (using `https://kovan.optimism.io` instead of localhost as the URL). The \"invalid sender\" error I believe is an instance of https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/issues/3961, so not on us.\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ curl -k -X POST -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"net_version\",\"id\":1}' https://kovan.optimism.io\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":\"1337\"}\r\n\r\n$ curl -k -X POST -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_chainId\",\"id\":1}' https://kovan.optimism.io\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":\"0x45\"}\r\n```",
